Machine Learning Engineer - Comment Team
Mountain ViewR&DExperienced
Responsibilities
TikTok is the leading destination for short-form mobile video. Our mission is to inspire creativity and bring joy. While fulfilling our mission, TikTok identifies trust and safety as a top priority.

In TikTok's Comment team, you’ll have the opportunity to build a modern machine learning system on our large-scale data. Our team is responsible for comment systems, content safety, and comment ranking to provide the best comment user experience for all TikTok users.

Responsibilities
Develop highly-scalable classifiers, models and algorithms, and tools to filter bad contents which violate our community guidelines;
Understand product objectives and take full advantage of modern machine learning and NLP techniques to improve comment user experience;
Work with cross-functional teams to deliver results.
Qualifications
1. Bachelor or higher degree in computer science or a related technical discipline, with 2+ years of industrial experience;
Solid experience in at least one of the following areas: machine learning, NLP, or data mining;
Solid coding skills and a good understanding of algorithms;
Great communication and teamwork skills;
Passion about techniques and solving challenging problems;
Experience in a popular open source machine learning platform is a plus.
